  "title": "Remove to-factory",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for participating in this project! We will try to answer as soon as possible 🙏\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe 🙏**\r\n\r\nWe don't use the advanced features of `to-factory`, so we don't need to rely on the dependency and its maintenance. Especially considering there's always some boilerplate at module boundaries\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like 🤔**\r\n\r\n```js\r\nconst instantsearch = options => new InstantSearch(options);\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered ✨**\r\n\r\nLeaving it as-is, spreading the options in case we have more than one argument\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/9632ade6434fb9257bdb23c66dde8aaa1c31c4eb/src/lib/main.js#L173\r\n",
